        </p>
        <p>Introduce students to goggles made and used by Indigenous peoples in Alaska to protect their eyes from sunlight reflecting off of snow (<url href="https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smithsonian-institution/snow-goggles-demonstrate-indigenous-ingenuity-180973738/"/>).</p>  
