      <example> <title>Standard MS-ESS3-1</title>
        <p>
          Description: Construct a scientific explanation based on evidence for how the uneven distributions of Earth's mineral, energy, and groundwater resources are the result of past and current geoscience processes.
        </p>
        <p><em>In-class:</em>Discuss how Rio Grande Rift processes (<url href="https://geoinfo.nmt.edu/publications/periodicals/litegeology/31/lg_v31.pdf"/>)  helped to form the Rio Grande and led to the fragmented distribution of aquifers in the Albuquerque Basin (<url href="https://www.riograndesierraclub.org/protect-albuquerque-basin-aquifer/"/>).   
        </p>
 
      </example>
        
      <example> <title>Standard MS-ESS2-1</title>
        <p>
