        <p>
          Description: Gather and synthesize information about technologies that have changed the way humans influence the inheritance of desired traits in organisms. 
        </p>
        <p><em>In-class and take home exercise:</em> Talk with students about how Native Americans bred different types of corn. Show videos located here: <url href="https://www.allaboutcorn.umn.edu/lessons/corn-breeding"/>. Talk with students about the different varieties of corn and other Native foods (<url href="https://www.nrcs.usda.gov/Internet/FSE_DOCUMENTS/nrcs141p2_015559.pdf"/>) and the importance of preserving these foods.        
</p>
      </example>   
        
